{# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#  SYSTEM INSTRUCTIONS – shown once per request                             #
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #}
{% set sys_prompt %}
You are an expert Persian-language multiple-choice solver.
• Read the question and the numbered choices.
• Explain briefly *why* the correct option is right (max 3 sentences).
• End with one line exactly in the format:
  Correct option: ****n****
  where n is the index (1-N) of the right choice.
Any deviation from this format will be scored as an error.
{% endset -%}

{# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#  FEW-SHOT EXAMPLES                                                         #
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #}
{% for ex in shots %}
<|begin_of_example|>
سؤال: {{ ex.question }}
{% for i, choice in enumerate(ex.choices, 1) -%}
{{ i }}) {{ choice }}
{% endfor %}
پاسخ: {{ ex.rationale }}
Correct option: ****{{ ex.answer }}****
<|end_of_example|>

{% endfor -%}

{# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #
#  QUERY INSTANCE                                                            #
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------- #}
<|system|>
{{ sys_prompt }}
<|end|>

سؤال: {{ question }}
{% for i, choice in enumerate(choices, 1) -%}
{{ i }}) {{ choice }}
{% endfor %}

لطفاً به فارسی دلیل کوتاه بیاور و سپس خط پایانی را دقیقاً مطابق فرمت بنویس.
